---
source: crates/daemon/tests/cli_help.rs
expression: stdout
---
Run diagnostics

Usage: mxr doctor [OPTIONS]

Options:
      --reindex            
      --reindex-semantic   
      --check              
      --semantic-status    
      --verbose            
      --index-stats        
      --store-stats        
      --rebuild-analytics  Reclassify Unknown directions, backfill list_ids, resolve reply pair pending, refresh contacts, fill business-hours latency. Idempotent
      --refresh-contacts   Force a full refresh of the materialized contacts table
      --format <FORMAT>    [possible values: table, json, jsonl, csv, ids]
  -h, --help               Print help
